OL,3,CArrests made in investigation into
OL,4,Cmemorial wall arson
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of arson over a fire at a
OL,8,Fmemorial wall in Golders Green, north
OL,9,FLondon, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,11,FA 46-year-old man and a 38-year-old
OL,12,Fwoman were arrested on Monday morning
OL,13,Fand taken to a London police station
OL,14,Fwhere they remain in custody.
OL,16,FThe arrests are part of an ongoing
OL,17,FCounter Terrorism Policing (CTP)
OL,18,Finvestigation following a reported
OL,19,Farson attack on a memorial wall in
OL,20,FLimes Avenue at around 1215am on April
OL,21,F27.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
