OL,3,CArrests made in investigation into
OL,4,Cmemorial wall arson
OL,6,FThe wall contains pictures of
OL,7,Fprotesters who were allegedly killed
OL,8,Fby the Iranian state in January.
OL,10,FThe wall incident is one of a number
OL,11,Fof suspected antisemitic arson attacks
OL,12,Fin the area being investigated by
OL,13,Fpolice in recent weeks.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
