OL,3,CArrests made in investigation into
OL,4,Cmemorial wall arson
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, Head of CTP
OL,7,FLondon, said: "We are committed to
OL,8,Fprotecting vulnerable communities in
OL,9,Fthe capital. Detectives have been
OL,10,Fconducting extensive inquiries since
OL,11,Fthis incident was reported to us last
OL,12,Fweek and these two arrests are the
OL,13,Fresult of that hard work."
